{"tid":1357984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「紅色警報」 網軍已經成功入侵連登！！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-23T23:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T05:50:16.000Z","uid":7971,"like":1132,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"2743f92a84b775b3c8cb9cdbbe1335b65560d749","tid":1357984,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:58:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個個就係你 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">依家個熱門系統係用view數區分<br />\n只要單新聞夠juicy 就click入去</span><br />\n唔睇內文 見人like就like<br />\n明明已經有人開同一件事post<br />\n但想自己個post多人睇 就開一個新<br />\n所以你都係幫凶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//上環天橋開槍有片，推上熱門！！！ 文宣文宣文宣！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357018//\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357018//</a><br />\n我依個post 頭1個鐘 都有接近900 like <br />\n但因為要推post 頁頁都只係推推推<br />\n咁討論啲咩啊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好叫「連登討論區」<br />\n叫「連登推post區」「連登風向區」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前一個post 推兩頁 就可以引發討論<br />\n有point嘅 就會多人討論 一齊傾先有行動 方向<br />\n<br />\n依家？<br />\n頁頁都係推推推 都上唔到熱門一<br />\n咁點討論啊？<br />\n仲要頁頁都只係回覆 推推推<br />\n咁仲係做到討論效果？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無咗個種 你有道理 就可以上熱門</span></span><br />\n咁係非常危險！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要有網軍 打手<br />\n同一時間集中推一個post <br />\n就可以制造風向</span></span><br />\n依個問題一定要解決！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">Admin請入一入黎，依家根本討論唔到！已經無咗你有道理 就可以上熱門</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357241\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357241</a><br />\n<br />\n見到嘅巴打 入依個post 一齊傾 一齊俾意見<br />\n唔好寫推 就咁一個推<br />\n個post 我哋要嘅係討論 同admin 一齊諗方法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">守住連登 守住依場運動！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7d01fc13716856a3f0f3962f547bbe314eb99a32","tid":1357984,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:58:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fab74ee8bd691bc8da0f209c326602f5e46f087","tid":1357984,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:59:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4346d73156f58b362da40a6b66eba4d5795b66b5","tid":1357984,"uid":242805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:59:48.000Z","msg":"推post要討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71409809fe69cb1399c9d9d9595ebd44a2a37899","tid":1357984,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"258ab9925188ddf22d843b28a0b8e8fc97fecd76","tid":1357984,"uid":7971,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:00:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">討論區要討論<br />\n已經失去 你有道理 就可以上熱門</span>"},{"pid":"5a48ed96001a503e23ce8ad0d5776997f2b8f0d5","tid":1357984,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:01:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">討論區要討論<br />\n已經失去 你有道理 就可以上熱門</span>"},{"pid":"29d09b81d098e87a16083c2162d4ee2d9c616613","tid":1357984,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4346d73156f58b362da40a6b66eba4d5795b66b5","tid":1357984,"uid":242805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:59:48.000Z","msg":"推post要討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:01:41.000Z","msg":"謝 幫推<br />\n<br />\n討論區要討論<br />\n已經失去 你有道理 就可以上熱門"},{"pid":"564eef6b7e44ca6f88f58e361883100fe74f059e","tid":1357984,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:01:53.000Z","msg":"討論區要討論<br />\n已經失去 你有道理 就可以上熱門"},{"pid":"5903cbc7