":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:51:36.000Z","msg":"唔該出post前double check，唔好同一個主題出十幾個po！！！！<br />\n<br />\n爆左先出另一個po<br />\n<br />\n寫明係集中po！一齊搵料一齊推！<br />\n覺得有用嘅留言推得大力啲！！"},{"pid":"dfecb63801aa3bccd1c8c4ddde0a21cbf719305c","tid":1357984,"uid":258561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:53:19.000Z","msg":"有道理嘅，但大家其實都係想重要資訊快啲上熱門比多啲人睇到先狂推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係要諗下點解決個問題，因為未必個個都咁有意見提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8c43423d4c366774f50742b44c97399a6476c7","tid":1357984,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:55:08.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖 連登真係奶左野"},{"pid":"e7588558972fb35dbc593f7e7c52f3837d99488d","tid":1357984,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adf13428442cace71aed5bf33f991297ec164707","tid":1357984,"uid":137593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:51:36.000Z","msg":"唔該出post前double check，唔好同一個主題出十幾個po！！！！<br />\n<br />\n爆左先出另一個po<br />\n<br />\n寫明係集中po！一齊搵料一齊推！<br />\n覺得有用嘅留言推得大力啲！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:55:16.000Z","msg":"就係大家其實都唔多唔少有私心 <br />\n想自己嘅post 上熱門 <br />\n其實人之常情<br />\n<br />\n但大事大非下 亂世下<br />\n同一類型post 可以洗哂板 <br />\n真係好影響後續"},{"pid":"fa805eac72698412c5eb560d7d0fd3e80144578e","tid":1357984,"uid":137593,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4ef49485b6451815bd2eb0a938ee8021cf1df8c1","tid":1357984,"uid":56984,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:22:25.000Z","msg":"正正想講好耐，成日都推，只要夠吸引嘅標題再加似真似假嘅內容就成功起風<br />\n<br />\n人嘅注意力得3-7分鐘，將個post推到3頁內就定曬生死，種下一個種子<br />\n<br />\n只要最後成功吸引多人睇，唔需要咩理性討論，多正評就已經帶到風向，真係希望admin諗諗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連仔/admin<br />\n<br />\n有冇得好似以前啲討論區咁<br />\n<br />\n1）最少要覆10/20/30個字？有冇得諗？？？<br />\n<br />\n確保係有用資訊而唔係一味9推<br />\n<br />\n2）有冇得加hashtag功能？？？<br />\n<br />\n比人出po前快啲check自己有冇重覆差唔多嘅資訊<br />\n<br />\n同埋<br />\n<br />\n唔該出post前double check，唔好同一個主題出十幾個po！！！！<br />\n<br />\n爆左先出另一個po<br />\n<br />\n寫明係集中po！一齊搵料一齊推！<br />\n覺得有用嘅留言推得大力啲！！"},{"pid":"c5031e562cd98eec7cc5c58c07c7c5c89ec66843","tid":1357984,"uid":75541,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:55:39.000Z","msg":"推呀屌！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdAqEQH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdAqEQH.png&h=9b40f637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>727元朗集中反黑</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">香港人絕不向黑勢力低頭！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但係！記住！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求！缺！一！不！可！<br />\n香港人！不！撤！不！散！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>義士不是condom！<br />\n說好的一個都不能少！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01iorVB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01iorVB.png&h=b7815076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑警於721，無人衝擊、毫無預警下<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>開槍</strong></span></span>！<br />\n總共開咗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">36槍！</span></span><br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係開槍！唔係扔彈呀！</span></strong></em><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果呢啖氣你都忍到嘅話，咁6月12號仲平乜撚嘢反？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求！</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n二、釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n三、撤回612暴動定性<br />\n四、追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n五、立即實行雙普選，還我真香港！</span><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;