夠成事<br />\n不過見到第一個回覆就係樓主自推, 就屌左一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868153ae94d94459da13068a3faa6931630021b8","tid":1357984,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fff02e57c35bae29f5704754b5e73edf6f374ece","tid":1357984,"uid":269780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:09:06.000Z","msg":"點解叫停地鐵不合作運動有兩個 posts 排頭位？<br />\n負評就唔覆嘛。<br />\n<br />\nPush"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"又一個例子！"},{"pid":"8fe10f7a1fc54702e77d449d77d9f3e82f8547f5","tid":1357984,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ad44e0520ec7942db038e35bdb6a1e6e22b2d9cb","tid":1357984,"uid":184514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:12:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">網軍真係有嚟到，啲濕鳩post都有40-60正皮！建議負到淨50負皮就夠加唔好覆，因為冇覆但大量負皮都會上熱門</span>"},{"pid":"c78f9a13330d96fecea0c99d9f4cbe053a0e4ec3","tid":1357984,"uid":216904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2743f92a84b775b3c8cb9cdbbe1335b65560d749","tid":1357984,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T23:58:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個個就係你 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">依家個熱門系統係用view數區分<br />\n只要單新聞夠juicy 就click入去</span><br />\n唔睇內文 見人like就like<br />\n明明已經有人開同一件事post<br />\n但想自己個post多人睇 就開一個新<br />\n所以你都係幫凶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//上環天橋開槍有片，推上熱門！！！ 文宣文宣文宣！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357018//\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357018//</a><br />\n我依個post 頭1個鐘 都有接近900 like <br />\n但因為要推post 頁頁都只係推推推<br />\n咁討論啲咩啊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好叫「連登討論區」<br />\n叫「連登推post區」「連登風向區」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前一個post 推兩頁 就可以引發討論<br />\n有point嘅 就會多人討論 一齊傾先有行動 方向<br />\n<br />\n依家？<br />\n頁頁都係推推推 都上唔到熱門一<br />\n咁點討論啊？<br />\n仲要頁頁都只係回覆 推推推<br />\n咁仲係做到討論效果？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無咗個種 你有道理 就可以上熱門</span></span><br />\n咁係非常危險！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要有網軍 打手<br />\n同一時間集中推一個post <br />\n就可以制造風向</span></span><br />\n依個問題一定要解決！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">Admin請入一入黎，依家根本討論唔到！已經無咗你有道理 就可以上熱門</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357241\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357241</a><br />\n<br />\n見到嘅巴打 入依個post 一齊傾 一齊俾意見<br />\n唔好寫推 就咁一個推<br />\n個post 我哋要嘅係討論 同admin 一齊諗方法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">守住連登 守住依場運動！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:15:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10dac0b4d4242c7c7ecf8074eda8a5754f007b48","tid":1357984,"uid":267321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:15:07.000Z","msg":"討論區要討論<br />\n已經失去 你有道理 就可以上熱門"},{"pid":"9cc7a82fedacf95c2be66f4c2de239c5442e4232","tid":1357984,"uid":96371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:22:27.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"010822f086a8d482cae1c2e1b7daa0a99921d99e","tid":1357984,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:22:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"221ce48776f83bab675ca8658686a87e85087fc1","tid":1357984,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:24:35.000Z","msg":"好多10幾分鐘一千正皮<br />\n果類post極危險"},{"pid":"efcf778ddb1814da9d2823e1cac0ebeaeef345a5","tid":1357984,"uid":272354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:25:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c899d5ab852701690f5f3d6d72bfe5a030f8dff3","tid":1357984,"uid":269780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:26:08.000Z","msg":"推到高過地鐵 posts<br />\n<br />\n負評就唔覆<br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"56d510274b6f005c9a58c95d181c1e94ab94966d","tid":1357984,"uid":271337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited